Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:23.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- GOOD MORNING, YUUJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.03,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S BEAUTIFUL OUTSIDE TODAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:29.49,Main,,0,0,0,,ARE YOU HUNGRY? HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:33.58,Main,,0,0,0,,YUUJI? YOU LOOK SLEEPY.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:36.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHOUKO, TOSS ME MY CELL.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.42,0:00:47.63,Main,,0,0,0,,HELLO, IS THIS THE POLICE?\NI'D LIKE TO REPORT AN INTRUDER.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:49.38,Main,,0,0,0,,( theme song playing )
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:19.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI, WHAT IS THIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, I DON'T KNOW. I'VE\NNEVER SEEN THAT BOOK BEFORE.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:27.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- REALLY? BECAUSE IT WAS HIDDEN\NUNDER A FALSE BOTTOM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.52,Main,,0,0,0,,IN THE THIRD DRAWER OF YOUR DESK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:32.03,Main,,0,0,0,,WITH A SCHOOLBOOK COVER\NDISGUISING IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:34.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- HELLO? DID YOU HAVE\NAN EMERGENCY? HELLO?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:38.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M SORRY. I MADE A MISTAKE.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:42.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- ALL RIGHT, IF YOU BURN IT,\NI WILL FORGIVE YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY WOULD I DO THAT? WHAT\NDO I CARE IF YOU FORGIVE ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:47.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- FINE. I'LL TAKE CARE\NOF IT MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:48.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU CAN'T JUST TORCH\NSOMEONE'S STUFF!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:53.47,Main,,0,0,0,,( Yuuji screams )
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,SO TELL ME WHAT ARE YOU DOING\NHERE ANYWAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:58.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- LET ME SHOW YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.89,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT. THE VIP TICKET\NFOR THE AMUSEMENT PARK?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.52,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW DID YOU GET THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- SOMEONE GENEROUS\NGAVE IT TO ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, RIGHT, SOMEONE GENEROUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.48,Main,,0,0,0,,AKIHISA WAS THE ONE\NWHO ENDED UP WITH THOSE TICKETS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:12.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- Akihisa: WASN'T ME.\NI'M NOT GUILTY!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:14.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE HAVE SPECIAL PASSES\NTO THE WEDDING EXPERIENCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.36,Main,,0,0,0,,( phone ringing )
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- Akihisa: HELLO?\NWHO MAY I ASK IS CALLING?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:21.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( in menacing tone )\NI'M GONNA KILL YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT? BUT WHY?\NWHO ARE YOU? PLEASE DON'T.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:26.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL. IT'S TIME. LET'S GO.\N- NO WAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO YOU LIED TO ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- I HAVE NO IDEA\NWHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:31.54,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU PROMISED THAT\NYOU WOULD GO OUT WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:33.71,Main,,0,0,0,,BACK WHEN YOU LOST THE ST WAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:36.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T REMEMBER THAT AT ALL.\N- IT'S YOUR CHOICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.26,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU SWORE IF YOU\NBROKE YOUR PROMISE,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:40.01,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU WOULD MARRY ME RIGHT AWAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:42.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY, NOW YOU'RE JUST\NMAKING THINGS UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( firecrackers exploding )
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- OF COURSE. THIS IS\NALL AKIHISA'S FAULT.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:48.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M GONNA KILL HIM.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:50.60,Main,,0,0,0,,ARGH! WOULD YOU LET GO?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.02,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW COME EVERY TIME YOU TOUCH ME\NIT HAS TO HURT?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:53.15,Main,,0,0,0,,- COUPLES ARE SUPPOSED TO WALK\NARM IN ARM LIKE THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:54.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- REALLY?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.70,Main,,0,0,0,,BECAUSE I DON'T SEE ANY OTHER\NCHICKS USING BRUTE FORCE!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- HELLO, LOVERS! WE'D LIKE TO\NGIVE YOU A BIG FAT WELCOME!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.00,Main,,0,0,0,,( phone ringing )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:08.79,Main,,0,0,0,,HELLO?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, YOU JERK WAD, I BET YOU\NGUYS THINK YOU'RE REALLY FUNNY,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:13.00,Main,,0,0,0,,DON'T YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:15.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- RUN! I'M INNOCENT!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:17.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- IF THAT'S TRUE, THEN WHY\NTHE HELL ARE YOU RUNNING?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU'RE A PART OF\NTHIS WHOLE THING TOO, HIDEYOSHI!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHO DID YOU SAY? I HAPPEN TO\NBE A MEMBER OF THE STAFF HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:33.61,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS IS MY OCCUPATION. I AM NOT\NACQUAINTED WITH THIS PERSON
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:35.40,Main,,0,0,0,,TO WHOM YOU ARE REFERRING.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- REALLY? I'M SUPPOSED\NTO BELIEVE THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.28,Main,,0,0,0,,( phone ringing )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH HEAVENS, MY HAND\NJUST SLIPPED FOR NO REASON.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:44.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- OF COURSE IT DID.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:47.91,Main,,0,0,0,,- MAY I PLEASE HAVE\NYOUR TICKETS NOW, FOLKS?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:50.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:53.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHOA! WOULD YOU LOOK AT THAT.\NYOU HAVE VIP PASSES WITH YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.84,Main,,0,0,0,,ALPHA CALLING BRAVO.\NI'VE CONFIRMED THE TARGET.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,WE HAVE A CODE SEVEN AND ARE\NSHIFTING TO OPERATION WEDDING.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.26,Main,,0,0,0,,REPEAT: OPERATION WEDDING.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:03.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE'RE STANDING RIGHT HERE.\NIT'S NOT LIKE WE CAN'T HEAR YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- PLEASE CALM DOWN, SIR.\NIT'S NOT YOUR CONCERN.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU WERE JUST\NTALKING ABOUT ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:09.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOW THEN,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.73,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S ABOUT TIME FOR US TO TAKE A\NCOMPLIMENTARY PICTURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:15.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- SMILE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHOUKO, SORRY!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.15,Main,,0,0,0,,AM I SUPPOSED TO NOT NOTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:25.20,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S YOU DOWN THERE BEING YOUR\NPERVERTED SELF?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,HEH!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:30.54,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI, BE NICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY, I'LL DO MY BEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- GOOD. I'LL REWARD YOU LATER.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:36.50,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO! HOW MANY TIMES\NDO I HAVE TO TELL YOU,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T GIVE A CRAP\NWHAT YOUR UNDERWEAR LOOKS LIKE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.34,Main,,0,0,0,,- Shouko: I WILL NEVER\NFORGIVE YOU FOR THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:44.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- STOP IT! PUSHING DOWN ON\NSOMEONE'S TEMPLES LIKE THAT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:45.80,Main,,0,0,0,,CAN CAUSE BRAIN DAMAGE!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- CHEESE!\N- Shouko: CHEESE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:53.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji: WHAT THE HELL\NIS THIS PICTURE?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S A FREE SOUVENIR\NFOR THE HAPPY COUPLE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:57.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'LL BE PUT UP IN\NTHE PARK'S PHOTO STUDIO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.32,Main,,0,0,0,,SO EVERYONE CAN SEE IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:01.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU CAN'T DO THAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:03.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI, DON'T BE SHY.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.78,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M NOT BEING SHY. I JUST\NDON'T WANT THIS PICTURE UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:08.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- COOL! CHECK IT OUT, BABY!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,LET'S HAVE THEM TAKE\NOUR PICTURE, TOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHATEVER YOU WANT, SUGAR.\NHEY, LITTLE DUDE!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:15.38,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU CAN GO AHEAD\NAND TAKE OUR PICTURE NEXT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:18.88,Main,,0,0,0,,- UNFORTUNATELY, GOOD SIR,\NTHIS SERVICE IS ONLY AVAILABLE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.80,Main,,0,0,0,,TO OUR VIP TICKET HOLDERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:24.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT? WE'RE CUSTOMERS, TOO,\NAND JUST ASKING FOR ONE PICTURE,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.39,Main,,0,0,0,,SO WHAT'S THE BIG DEAL?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:28.56,Main,,0,0,0,,WOULDN'T YOU RATHER HAVE\NA HOT COUPLE ON DISPLAY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,INSTEAD OF\NTHOSE LAME TWEENIES. WELL?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:35.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S TRUE. I MEAN, LOOK AT US.\NIT'S NOT LIKE HIGH SCHOOL KIDS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,CAN COMPARE, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:41.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOLD ON.\NWHERE ARE YOU GOING?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WILL NOT ALLOW THEM\NTO TALK THAT WAY ABOUT US.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:46.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- DON'T LET THOSE JERKS\NGET TO YOU, OKAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- ALL RIGHT THEN,\NIF THAT'S WHAT YOU WANT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:50.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE WANT TO HAVE A PICTURE\NJUST LIKE THEY HAD!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- ALL RIGHT. IF YOU INSIST,\NWE'LL DO IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:54.46,Main,,0,0,0,,PLEASE COME THIS WAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:57.79,Main,,0,0,0,,IF YOU COULD PUT YOUR HAND\NRIGHT HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.54,Main,,0,0,0,,NOW, SQUEEZE AS HARD AS YOU CAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.42,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( man groans )
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.88,Main,,0,0,0,,- CHEESE.\N- Girl: CHEESE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:05.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT THE HELL\NDO YOU THINK YOU'RE DOING?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.59,Main,,0,0,0,,- SAID YOU WANTED US\NTO TAKE THE SAME PICTURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:10.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- I HOPE YOU RUN FAST,\N'CAUSE I'M GONNA KILL YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- GO-GO! BURGER HEAD'S\NLOST HIS MIND!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- ARE YOU MAKING FUN OF ME,\NYOU PUNK?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- WOULD YOU LIKE FRIES\NWITH THAT, SIR?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- OF COURSE. YOU KNOW, IF\NYOU WANTED TO LEAVE INTSEAD,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:25.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I'D BE COOL WITH IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.74,Main,,0,0,0,,DOESN'T IT BOTHER YOU AT ALL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:29.37,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT EVERYONE CAN SEE\NWHAT YOU'RE DOING TO ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:31.08,Main,,0,0,0,,- DON'T BE SHY. RELAX.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M NOT BEING SHY, I JUST\NPREFER NOT BE HURTING!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT THIS IS HOW COUPLES WALK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S ARM IN ARM,\NNOT ARM IN PAIN!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:41.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- GREETINGS TO THE ADORABLE\NLOOKING COUPLE OVER THERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:45.59,Main,,0,0,0,,- SEE. I TOLD YOU\NWE LOOKED LIKE A COUPLE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHE'S A GIANT FUZZ BALL.\NWHAT DOES SHE KNOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- I AM FEE THE FOX.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:52.35,Main,,0,0,0,,PLEASE ALLOW ME TO SHOW YOU A\NFUN AND INTERESTING ATTRACTION.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- EARLIER I COULD'VE SWORN\NAKIHISA WAS OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.60,Main,,0,0,0,,ON A DATE WITH SOME CHICK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:08:00.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT? YOU SAW YOSHII?\NWHERE IS HE? WHERE DID THEY GO?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:01.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- HELLO, THERE, HIMEJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:05.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( train whistle toots )
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- I AM FEE THE FOX.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:12.62,Main,,0,0,0,,PLEASE ALLOW ME TO SHOW YOU A\NFUN AND INTERESTING ATTRACTION.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.83,Main,,0,0,0,,- LOOK, IF YOU WANT TO PLAY\NINNOCENT, THAT'S FINE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:18.04,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DON'T YOU JUST TELL US WHERE\NWE SHOULD GO THEN, ALL RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,OKAY! DON'T MISS THE HAUNTED\NHOUSE RIGHT OVER THERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:22.92,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU SHOULD GO NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- AWESOME. SHOUKO, WE'RE GOING\NANYWHERE BUT THAT HAUNTED HOUSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:29.97,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT! YOU HAVE TO GO!\NWHY DON'T YOU WANNA?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- BECAUSE I'M SURE YOU GUYS HAVE\NSET UP SOMETHING STUPID THERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:35.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- PLEASE! GO TO\NTHE HAUNTED HOUSE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:37.60,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU DON'T WANT TO MISS OUT\NON IT! PLEASE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:39.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOT HAPPENING.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- STOP RIGHT THERE, YUUJI!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:44.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M NOIN, AND I WILL NOT\NLET YOU MAKE FEE CRY ANYMORE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:47.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, COME ON, YOUR HEAD'S\NALL MESSED UP, AKIHISA.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:50.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOW RUDE!\NWHICH PART IS MESSED UP?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:53.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI, NOIN IS\NTHE ABSENTMINDED ONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:54.95,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T CARE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.95,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT KINDA FOX WOULD HAVE\NHIS HEAD ON BACKWARDS?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:59.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOSHII! YOU PUT YOUR HEAD ON\NTHE WRONG WAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT? DAMN IT! NO WONDER\NI COULDN'T SEE ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- HURRY AND FIX IT BEFORE THEY\NFIGURE OUT WHO WE ARE!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- Akihisa: WHAT'S HAPPENING?\NWHERE AM I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:08.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- THE SAD THING IS, THEY REALLY\NTHINK THEY'VE FOOLED US.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.26,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, BY THE WAY,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:13.97,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW DID YOUR DATE WITH THAT\NSUPER HOT COLLEGE CHICK GO, MAN?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:15.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:20.81,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOSHII, I HEARD\NWHILE WE WERE WORKING
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,ON THIS VERY\NIMPORTANT ASSIGNMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.61,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT YOU WENT OUT ON A DATE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:27.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT. WHERE'D YOU HEAR THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- MINAMI'S ON HER WAY\NHERE NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:32.61,Main,,0,0,0,,WE THINK WE NEED TO SIT DOWN\NAND TALK ABOUT IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:35.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO! BAD IDEA. THIS PARK IS\NSUPPOSED TO BE FOR AMUSEMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,NOT A-FIGHTING!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:39.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY! WHAT THE HELL\NIS GOING ON HERE, AKI?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOW'D SHE GET HERE SO FAST?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.59,Main,,0,0,0,,TRASH CAN! AND GROUND!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:48.42,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE GONNA TELL US\NEVERY SINGLE DETAIL.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.59,Main,,0,0,0,,- AND YOU NEED TO TELL US\NTHE TRUTH, TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:53.30,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T KNOW WHAT'S GOING ON.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.64,Main,,0,0,0,,- LET'S GET OUT OF HERE, SHOUKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.05,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT DO YOU SAY WE GO RIDE\NTHE FERRIS WHEEL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.43,Main,,0,0,0,,OR SOMETHING LIKE THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.93,Main,,0,0,0,,SHOUKO? WHERE'D YOU...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( dramatic music playing )
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:03.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- EVERYTHING SET UP,\NTHE HAUNTED HOUSE IS READY.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- STOP THAT!\N- WE'RE GOING WHERE THEY WANT.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:11.49,Main,,0,0,0,,- AH, WHAT THE HELL\NDID HIDEYOSHI SAY TO YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT I CAN JUMP INTO\NYOUR ARMS IN THERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,- SIGN THIS BEFORE ENTERING.\N- SIGN WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:22.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- LIABILITY WAIVER.\NSUCH WAIVERS ARE OFTEN PREPARED
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,IN THESE TYPES OF DANGEROUS\NSITUATIONS. JUST IN CASE.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- REALLY? SO THIS PLACE IS\NACTUALLY DANGEROUS?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.59,Main,,0,0,0,,AT LEAST THAT'LL\NMAKE IT INTERESTING.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:35.26,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT'S IT SAY?\NWAIVER: I, YUUJI SAKAMOTO,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:37.39,Main,,0,0,0,,WILL LOVE SHOUKO KIRISHIMA\NAS MY WIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:40.18,Main,,0,0,0,,AS LONG AS I LIVE AND WILL SHARE\NMY JOYS AND SORROWS WITH HER.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,SO I SWEAR?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:44.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- HERE'S A PEN.\N- AND A REGISTERED SEAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- INK PAD TO STAMP IT WITH.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:47.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT THE HELL?\NAM I THE ONLY ONE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.61,Main,,0,0,0,,WHO FINDS THIS\NENTIRE THING RIDICULOUS?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:51.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- UNDER THE CARBON SHEET\NIS A SECOND SHEET,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:53.61,Main,,0,0,0,,YOUR MARRIAGE REGISTRATION FORM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:55.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOW CONSIDERATE.\N- NO, IT ISN'T!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- Shouko: BAKA AND TEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- PLEASE, COME THIS WAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:09.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- WOULD YOU MIND\NHOLDING MY BAG FOR ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- MAKE SURE WHAT'S INSIDE\NDOESN'T FALL OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:13.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- AS YOU WISH.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.88,Main,,0,0,0,,WELL THEN, I HOPE YOU ENJOY\NYOURSELVES
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:18.05,Main,,0,0,0,,WHILST BEING\NTHOROUGHLY TERRIFIED.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:19.14,Main,,0,0,0,,( finger snaps )
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( eerie music playing )
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:27.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO THIS IS SUPPOSED TO BE\NAN ABANDONED HOSPITAL?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:29.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I GUESS IT'S NOT\NTOO BAD, CONSIDERING...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:31.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- Recorded voice: HIMEJI...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:32.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT'S THAT?\N- THAN SHOUKO...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.78,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT SOUNDS LIKE YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- HIMEJI'S MORE THAN...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:38.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- WEIRD. IT'S LIKE SYNTHESIZED.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:40.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I WONDER\NIF HIDEYOSHI'S DOING IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHATEVER. IT'S NOT\NSCARY AT ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- HIMEJI IS MORE MY TYPE\NTHAN SHOUKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:47.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT... WHAT?\N- SHE'S GOT BIGGER BOOBIES, TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:49.08,Main,,0,0,0,,HIMEJI IS MORE MY\NTYPE THAN SHOUKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,SHE'S GOT BIGGER BOOBIES, TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.67,Main,,0,0,0,,HIMEJI'S MORE MY TYPE\NTHAN SHOUKO...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:56.55,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI, IS THAT TRUE?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY, GUYS! VERY FUNNY!\NYOU GOT ME. I'M SCARED.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:07.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI, PREPARE YOURSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:10.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- CRAP! WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?\NSHE'S REALLY GONNA HURT ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- PLEASE CALM DOWN!\NIT'S JUST A TRICK!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:15.49,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( girl screams )
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:18.15,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( breathing heavily )
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:19.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOW DID IT GO?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I BET THAT RIDE MADE YOU WANT\NTO GET MARRIED, DIDN'T IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:23.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT MAKES YOU THINK\NI'D WANT TO GET MARRIED?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- BECAUSE THEY SAY WHEN A MAN\NAND A WOMAN FACE DANGER TOGETHER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:28.54,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT COUPLE FORMS\NA SPECIAL BOND.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT ONLY WORKS WHEN ONE\NOF THEM ISN'T THE DANGER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:31.58,Main,,0,0,0,,THE OTHER ONE IS FACING!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:34.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI, I THINK\NIT'S LUNCHTIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:37.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- FINE. ALL THAT RUNNING AROUND\NMADE ME HUNGRY ANYWAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:39.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( music on PA )
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:43.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara on PA: UM, ATTENTION,\NGUESTS, ATTENTION GUESTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,WE'VE PREPARED A SPECIAL MENU\NFOR THOSE WITH A VIP TICKET
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:48.48,Main,,0,0,0,,AT THE RESTAURANT TODAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:52.90,Main,,0,0,0,,AND DURING LUNCH, A SPECIAL\NPERFORMANCE WILL BE HELD.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:55.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- NICE. A SPECIAL MENU.\N- FOLLOW US TO THE RESTAURANT.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:56.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- RIGHT THIS WAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:58.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT'S THE MATTER, SHOUKO?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOTHING. I'M JUST\NREALLY HUNGRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:04.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- ME, TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.21,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT WAS PRETTY GOOD, HUH?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:11.83,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M WITH YOU,\NOF COURSE IT WAS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:15.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( both gasp )
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:16.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- GOOD AFTERNOON, EVERYONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:19.88,Main,,0,0,0,,THANK YOU SO MUCH FOR COMING TO\NOUR SPECIAL PERFORMANCE TODAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- BELIEVE IT OR NOT, WE ACTUALLY\NHAVE A BEAUTIFUL YOUNG COUPLE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:25.14,Main,,0,0,0,,DINING WITH US WHO\NARE VERY EXCITED
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.60,Main,,0,0,0,,ABOUT GETTING MARRIED SOON!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- EXCUSE ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:30.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- IN THEIR HONOR, WE'VE ARRANGED\NA GAME TO CELEBRATE THEIR UNION
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,AND TO SHOW OUR SUPPORT!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:34.73,Main,,0,0,0,,GET READY, EVERYONE,\NBECAUSE IT'S TIME FOR
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,THE SUPER DELUXE GRAND\NWEDDING EXPERIENCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- YAY! LET THE SHOW BEGIN!\NEVERYONE CHEER!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- DAMN IT! THEY'VE LOCKED\NTHE EXIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:44.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- IF THEY ANSWER THE FOLLOWING\NFIVE QUESTIONS CORRECTLY,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:46.20,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY'LL BE ABLE\NTO EXPERIENCE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,OUR EXCITING AND ROMANTIC\NWEDDING PACKAGE!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:51.33,Main,,0,0,0,,AND IF THEY WANT TO GO AHEAD\NAND GET MARRIED AT THE TIME,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WON'T BE A PROBLEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, IT'S A PROBLEM!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- WILL MISTER YUUJI SAKAMOTO\NAND THE LOVELY MISS SHOUKO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.67,Main,,0,0,0,,PLEASE HEAD TOWARD THE STAGE?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, WE WON'T!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:01.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- WEDDING EXPERIENCE?\NWE WILL NOT FAIL.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S A DREAM COME TRUE!\N- LET GO OF ME, SHOUKO!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.55,Main,,0,0,0,,- AREN'T YOU EXCITED?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:06.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- THIS BLOWS.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I HAVE GOT TO FIND A WAY\NTO GET OUT OF HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- ALL RIGHT,\NLET THE QUIZ BEGIN!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:13.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- OF COURSE! WE HAVE TO ANSWER\NTHE QUESTIONS CORRECTLY!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.56,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS WILL BE A PIECE OF CAKE\NTO LOSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:17.57,Main,,0,0,0,,ALL I HAVE TO DO IS GIVE\NTHE WRONG ANSWER!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:19.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- QUESTION NUMBER ONE!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:22.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- BRING IT ON! I'VE GOT\NTHIS THING IN THE BAG!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHEN IS MISTER YUUJI SAKAMOTO\NAND MISS SHOUKO'S ANNIVERSARY?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:31.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY, I DON'T THINK I\NUNDERSTAND WHAT THEY'RE ASKING.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- I KNOW.\NIT IS EVERY DAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:39.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- CORRECT! EVERY DAY IS AN\NANNIVERSARY! GOOD JOB, LOVERS!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.46,Main,,0,0,0,,QUESTION NUMBER TWO!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M GONNA GIVE THEM\NSUCH A WRONG ANSWER,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:43.59,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY WON'T\NKNOW WHAT HIT 'EM.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:46.39,Main,,0,0,0,,- TELL US WHERE ARE YOU GOING\NTO HOLD YOUR WEDDING?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.47,0:14:48.97,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( beeping )\N- MACKEREL COOKED IN MISO!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT IS CORRECT!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:52.39,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( audience cheering )\N- IS NOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- IS TO! YOU'VE PLANNED TO\NHAVE YOUR UPCOMING WEDDING
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:57.56,Main,,0,0,0,,HELD IN THE PHOENIX HALL WHICH\NHAS RECENTLY BEEN NICKNAMED
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.44,Main,,0,0,0,,"MACKEREL COOKED IN MISO"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT ARE YOU\NTALKING ABOUT?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.40,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU JUST NICKNAMED IT\NTHAT, DIDN'T YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:03.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- Akihisa: QUESTION\NNUMBER THREE!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:05.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOW I GET WHAT YOU'RE DOING.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:09.66,Main,,0,0,0,,THERE'S NO WAY YOU'LL BE ABLE TO\NMAKE MY NEXT ANSWER WORK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:11.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHERE DID YOU TWO\NMEET THE FIRST TIME?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- I GOT IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:16.71,Main,,0,0,0,,( screams )
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:19.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- GRADE SCHOOL.\N- THAT'S CORRECT!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:23.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- FINE! I'LL GIVE UP BEFORE\NTHEY CAN EVEN ASK IT THIS TIME!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:26.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- AND NOW FOR QUESTION NUMBER\NFOUR! THE TWO OF YOU...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T KNOW!\N- CORRECT.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:31.35,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S NO USE.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:34.56,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY WON'T LET MY ANSWERS BE\NWRONG NO MATTER WHAT I DO.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.35,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS IS THE END FOR ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.15,Main,,0,0,0,,- HELLO! NOT FAIR!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:40.61,Main,,0,0,0,,WE ARE PLANNING TO GET MARRIED,\NTOO, YOU KNOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:41.77,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY ARE THEY THE ONLY ONES
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.11,Main,,0,0,0,,WHO GET THE SPECIAL FANCY\NTREATMENT, HUH?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH. WE WANNA PLAY\NYOUR STUPID GAME.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:51.49,Main,,0,0,0,,- LOOK, BURGER HEAD... I MEAN,\NSIR, WE'RE NOT DONE YET.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOW YOU LISTEN TO ME,\NYOU STUPID FOX.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:58.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M A CUSTOMER, TOO! YOU JERK!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:01.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- HE'S RIGHT, YOU KNOW.\NWE WANT A WEDDING THINGIE.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.21,Main,,0,0,0,,AND WE SHOULD BE ABLE\NTO HAVE IT, TOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, YEAH, BUT...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.55,Main,,0,0,0,,- DON'T GIVE ME THAT\N"WELL, YEAH BUT" CRAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,WE'RE GONNA DO IT,\NSO JUST GIVE US WHAT WE WANT!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:11.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH MY GOD, YOU GUYS,\NI'M SO SMART! I HAVE AN IDEA!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:13.85,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DON'T WE ASK THE\NLAST QUESTION.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:15.43,Main,,0,0,0,,IF THEY GET IT RIGHT, THEY WIN,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.23,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT IF THEY GET IT WRONG, WE DO!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:18.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T THINK THAT'LL WORK.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:21.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- PERFECT! I KNOW I'LL BE\NABLE TO ANSWER THEM WRONG.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,THEN I CAN FINALLY GET OUT OF\NTHIS WHOLE WEDDING NIGHTMARE!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- ALL RIGHT. LISTEN UP, KIDS,\NHERE'S THE QUESTION!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:32.24,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT'S THE CAPITOL CITY\NOF EUROPE?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:33.91,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( all mumbling )
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:43.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- CONGRATULATIONS! MISTER YUUJI\NSAKAMOTO AND MISS SHOUKO HAVE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:46.72,Main,,0,0,0,,WON THE EXCLUSIVE\NWEDDING EXPERIENCE!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- AND NOW WE'D LIKE TO PRESENT\NTODAY'S MAIN EVENT!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:56.22,Main,,0,0,0,,THE WEDDING\NSTARRING YUUJI AND SHOUKO!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:17:00.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- FIRST, LET'S WELCOME OUR GROOM\NWITH A WARM ROUND OF APPLAUSE!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( audience cheering )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:08.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU REALIZE I'M GONNA KNOCK\NYOUR TEETH OUT FOR THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- AND NEXT,\NTHE GROOMS PROFILE!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:14.08,Main,,0,0,0,,WE DON'T HAVE THIS PART READY\NYET, SO WE'LL JUST SKIP IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:19.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- FINALLY! WELCOME THE BRIDE AS\NSHE MAKES HER GRAND ENTRANCE!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( mellow music playing )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:38.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( Yuuji gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:39.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHE LOOKS SO PRETTY!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- UM, YUUJI?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:49.86,Main,,0,0,0,,TELL ME THE TRUTH. DO YOU REALLY\NTHINK THAT I LOOK LIKE A BRIDE?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:51.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- ALL THINGS CONSIDERED,\NYOU LOOK PRETTY NICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I MEAN I'VE DEFINITELY SEEN\NWORSE OUT THERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.54,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI?\N- YEAH, WHAT IS IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:00.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M SO HAPPY.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT... DON'T CRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:07.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- THIS IS A DREAM COME TRUE.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:09.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- A DREAM?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WANTED THIS SINCE...\NSINCE WE WERE KIDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I PRAYED FOR THIS MOMENT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:16.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I'VE ALWAYS DREAMED\NOF BEING ABLE TO MARRY YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I DREAMED THAT ONE DAY\NI WOULD GET TO BE THE BRIDE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:20.27,Main,,0,0,0,,OF YUUJI SAKAMOTO.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I NEVER THOUGHT IT\NWOULD ACTUALLY HAPPEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.60,Main,,0,0,0,,AND HERE WE ARE.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:26.23,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU AND I,\NSTANDING LIKE THIS TOGETHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M JUST REALLY HAPPY RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,AFTER ALL, I'M HERE WITH YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:33.61,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS DAY IS EVERYTHING\NI'VE EVER HOPED FOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHOUKO, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, MAN. THIS IS BORING!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:43.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( grunting )
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:45.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- CAN SOMEONE DO SOMETHING\NINTERESTING, PLEASE?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.88,Main,,0,0,0,,NO ONE CARES ABOUT\NYOUR LOSER LOVE LIFE.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:50.21,Main,,0,0,0,,SO HURRY UP, SO WE CAN\NGET THIS THING OVER WITH!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, WE'VE GOT STUFF TO DO,\NYOU KNOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:54.09,Main,,0,0,0,,ENOUGH WITH THE CHIT CHAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.85,Main,,0,0,0,,SHUT UP ALREADY AND GET\NTO THE FREAKIN' POINT!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- DOES ANYONE ELSE\NTHINK IT'S WEIRD
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.60,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT HER DREAM IS\NTO BECOME A BRIDE?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:01.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, WHAT,\NSHE'S LIKE TWELVE, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:03.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOT TO BE RUDE,\NBUT THAT IS WAY CREEPY.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:06.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- MAYBE WE'RE ON ONE OF THOSE\NPRACTICAL JOKE SHOWS?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( both laughing )
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- Girl: C'MON!\NWHERE ARE THE CAMERAS?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:12.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DARE YOU TO SAY THAT AGAIN!\NWHAT DO YOU CARE?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.36,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DO YOU TWO\NHAVE TO BE SO RUDE?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:17.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I THINK YOU BETTER GET OUT OF\NHERE BEFORE I KICK YOU OUT. SO.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:19.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT, YOSHII!\N- WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE ABOUT TO MESS UP\NTHE ENTIRE EVENT!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.91,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT THEY... THEY WERE\NSO MEAN TO SHOUKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,-I CAN'T JUST DO NOTHING!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji: SHOUKO...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- (people chattering )
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:38.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( panting )
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.01,Main,,0,0,0,,- Mizuki: YOSHII!\NDID YOU SEE HER ANYWHERE?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:42.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- Akihisa: SHE DIDN'T\NGO THIS WAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- Hideyoshi: YUUJI!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:50.52,Main,,0,0,0,,WHERE DID SHOUKO GO?\N- Yuuji: I DON'T KNOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:51.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY NOT?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:52.78,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, DO YOU KNOW WHERE\NSHE MIGHT BE?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:54.49,Main,,0,0,0,,EVERYONE'S REALLY\NWORRIED ABOUT HER.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M NOT. I DON'T CARE.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( all gasping )
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T HAVE TIME FOR THIS.\NI HAVE TO GO TO THE BATHROOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:00.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- Mizuki: YOU HAVE TO WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:02.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I HAVE TO PEE. SEE YA.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT WEDDING WAS A JOKE.\NTALK ABOUT TOTAL CRAP, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:09.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I MEAN LOOK AT THE COUPLE.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:12.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, YUUJI, I'VE ALWAYS\NDREAMED OF MARRYING YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:14.21,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW'S THAT? SOUND LIKE HER?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:17.47,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, YOU REALLY DO. THAT WAS\NPERFECT. SHE WAS SO PATHETIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:19.01,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( both laughing )
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.39,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, YOU TWO.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.68,0:20:23.35,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT THE HELL DO YOU WANT,\NHIGH SCHOOL BOY?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:26.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, IT'S REALLY NOT\NTHAT BIG OF A DEAL, BUT...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:27.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:30.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- I THINK THE THREE OF US\NNEED TO HAVE A TALK!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji: HEY.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I WAS BEGINNING TO WONDER\NIF YOU'D SHOW UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:48.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?\N- I FIGURED YOU'D COME HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:53.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI...\N- WHAT IS IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:56.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- DO YOU THINK\NMY DREAM IS WEIRD?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:02.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHOUKO, THERE'S SOMETHING\NI REALLY NEED TO SAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.72,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU SHOULDN'T FEEL THE WAY\NTHAT YOU DO ABOUT ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.85,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S A BIG MISTAKE.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:09.27,Main,,0,0,0,,SEVEN YEARS AGO, I WAS STUPID.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,AND YOU GOT SUCKED INTO\NALL THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:14.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I WAS ONLY EVER TRYING TO TAKE\NRESPONSIBILITY, THAT'S ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:16.23,Main,,0,0,0,,NOTHING ELSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:18.78,Main,,0,0,0,,ALL THIS TIME YOU'VE BEEN\NWASTING YOUR DREAMS ON ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.65,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I KNOW I'M NOT WORTH IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:22.49,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( Shouko whimpers )
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- BELIEVE ME. I'M REALLY SORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:27.83,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- LISTEN TO ME. YOUR DREAM\NIS NOTHING TO LAUGH AT!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:36.09,Main,,0,0,0,,YEAH, YOU MAY HAVE PICKED\NTHE WRONG GUY,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:38.26,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I THINK CARING ABOUT SOMEONE\NFOR SUCH A LONG TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:40.26,Main,,0,0,0,,IS A WONDERFUL THING.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:43.26,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT YOU WANT IS AMAZING,\NAND YOU SHOULD BE PROUD OF IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:45.18,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT'S WHAT MAKES YOU\NSO SPECIAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:48.60,Main,,0,0,0,,ALTHOUGH, YOU PROBABLY WANT TO\NGO WITH THE RIGHT MAN NEXT TIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:52.77,Main,,0,0,0,,IT MIGHT WORK OUT BETTER.\N( chuckles )
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:55.77,Main,,0,0,0,,WELL, THEN, GUESS IT'S NOT EVERY\NDAY YOU ALMOST GET MARRIED.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU MIGHT AS WELL HAVE SOME KIND\NOF SOUVENIR FROM IT, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:21:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT, YUUJI, WAIT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:03.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, YEAH! I ALMOST FORGOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:04.95,Main,,0,0,0,,THANKS FOR THAT\NLUNCH YOU MADE.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.03,0:22:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS DELICIOUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:09.54,Main,,0,0,0,,LET'S GO HOME.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.62,0:22:11.83,Main,,0,0,0,,IF IT GETS ANY LATER, PEOPLE\NWILL THINK WE'RE TOGETHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:13.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.75,0:22:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:19.34,Main,,0,0,0,,- I KNEW IT. I KNEW THERE WAS NO\NWAY I COULD BE WRONG ABOUT YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.26,0:22:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( theme song playing )
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:53.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara: QUESTION 8:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.68,0:23:56.64,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT DOES 'COMPUTER' REFER TO\NIN THE JAPANESE LANGUAGE?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.73,0:23:58.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- Akihisa: SUPER\NELECTRONIC BRAIN!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:23:59.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT SOUNDS PRETTY TOUGH.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.86,0:24:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- NEXT TIME: LOSS OF CONTROL,\NLABYRINTHS,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.61,0:24:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THE AVATAR\NINSTRUMENTALITY PROJECT!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.82,0:24:05.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- THIS WILL BE ON THE TEST.
